OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780081925
OL,3,CWoman arrested after man's body found
OL,4,Cin a van parked in city centre
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after a man's body was found
OL,8,Fin a van parked in a city centre.
OL,10,FPolice were called to a car park on
OL,11,FGarden Street, in the centre of
OL,12,FLeicester, just after 5.30pm on
OL,13,FWednesday, 27 May after a member of
OL,14,Fthe public reported concern about the
OL,15,Fcondition of a van.
OL,17,FWhen officers forced entry to the
OL,18,Fvehicle, the body of a man was found
OL,19,Finside. Police are working to locate
OL,20,Fthe man's next of kin.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
