PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780081925
OL,3,CWoman arrested after man's body found
OL,4,Cin a van parked in city centre
OL,6,FAfter finding the address of the
OL,7,Fregistered keeper of the van, further
OL,8,Finquiries led to the arrest of a 39-
OL,9,Fyear-old woman.
OL,11,FShe was arrested at a property in
OL,12,FHounslow on suspicion of murder and
OL,13,Fremains in custody.
OL,15,FLeicestershire Police said an
OL,16,Finvestigation to establish the
OL,17,Fcircumstances that led to the man's
OL,18,Fdeath are continuing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
