FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780081925
OL,3,CWoman arrested after man's body found
OL,4,Cin a van parked in city centre
OL,6,FDet Insp Kev Hames, from the East
OL,7,FMidlands Special Operations Unit's
OL,8,Fmajor crime team, said: "I'd like to
OL,9,Fspeak to anyone who can help with our
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,F"The man was found in a white Ford
OL,13,FTransit with the registration BF18 VNV.
OL,15,F"Officers are appealing for anyone who
OL,16,Fmay have seen this van in Garden
OL,17,FStreet or other parts of Leicester and
OL,18,FLeicestershire to get in touch.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780081925
OL,3,CWoman arrested after man's body found
OL,4,Cin a van parked in city centre
OL,6,F"This includes anyone who may have
OL,7,Fseen the van where they live or work
OL,8,Fto get in touch. I'd like to extend
OL,9,Fthis appeal to anyone who may have
OL,10,Fcaptured its movements on CCTV or a
OL,11,Fdashcam."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
